<h1>Placeholder checkout view.</h1>
<p>This page may end up in orders/index or something similar.</p>
<p>Display list of cart items, much like the carts/index page.</p>
<p>Gather all of the session and product data and create Order and OrderItem entries.</p>
<p>The only thing that will need to be passed to Stripe is the total on the order, in cents.</p>


<%= form_tag charges_path do %>
  <article>
    <% if flash[:error].present? %>
      <div id="error_explanation">
        <p><%= flash[:error] %></p>
      </div>
    <% end %>
    <label class="amount">
      <span>Amount: $5.00</span>
    </label>
  </article>

  <script src="https://checkout.stripe.com/checkout.js" class="stripe-button"
          data-key="<%= Rails.configuration.stripe[:publishable_key] %>"
          data-description="A month's subscription"
          data-amount="500"
          data-locale="auto"></script>
<% end %>
